      Digilent's Nexys Video SoC based on LiteX

[> Getting started
1. Install Python3 and your vendor's software

2. Obtain LiteX and install it:
  git clone https://github.com/enjoy-digital/litex --recursive
  cd litex
  python3 setup.py develop
  cd ..

3. Obtain LiteEth and install it:
  git clone https://github.com/enjoy-digital/liteeth
  cd liteeth
  python3 setup.py develop
  cd ..

4. Obtain LiteScope and install it:
  git clone https://github.com/enjoy-digital/litescope
  cd litescope
  python3 setup.py develop
  cd ..

5. Build the gateware and software:
  make nexys_minisoc
  make load

[> Status:
BaseSoC (DDR3 and SPI still missing).

